msgid ""
"The Outline effect adds a customizable border around images or text within a "
"video frame. It works by extracting the image’s alpha channel, blurring it "
"to generate a smooth outline mask, and then combining this mask with a solid "
"color layer. Users can adjust the outline’s width as well as its color "
